Realty ONE Group Mountain Desert Sedona

data.description: Creekside living! This custom built home located on Spring Creek sits on a third of an acre. Relax on the beautiful back deck and enjoy the views of the creek and wildlife! There are 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, along with a carpeted 10X16 loft that could be used for storage, a craft room, etc. There is also an Arizona room off of the back of the house that is heated and cooled. For your convenience, there is a dumb waiter to bring your groceries right up to the main living area. Its is within minutes of Cottonwood, Jerome and Sedona. Shopping is close as well. Come see this wonderful home soon!
